"Pours thick and dark with a brownish head. Wow-chocolate jumps from the glass. First sip tells you this is something to be savored. Velvety mouthfeel, and full, deep, rich flavor. This beer is decadent. I don't think I could drink more than 1 (okay 3) in a sitting. The vanilla character complements the chocolate and sweet lactose flavor very well. Wish is was a bit drier, rather than sweet, but after all, it is a milk stout. Chocolate Milk for adults is the best way to describe this beer. Find it!"
